text: haey chaur puok anak som aphytosa pi mcheasa robsa puok anak banteab mk chaur puok anak sarphap kamhosa champoh trong del trong nung phdal aoy puok anak nouv pheap rikreay da brapei rhautadl pelvelea muoy delke ban kamnt . haey trong nung phdal aoy real anak del mean pheap khpangkhpasa nouv utdamphap robsa ke . bo nde brasenbae puok anak berchenh vinh pitabrakd nasa khnhom baromph champoh puok anak nouv tearounakamm nea thngai da mhema( thngai br- lok)
